**Delegate Pattern**

```
public interface IOrder {
    int getDaysToShip();
}

public class Order : IOrder {
    protected Warehouse _warehouse;

    @Override
    public int getDaysToShip() {
        return _warehouse.getDaysToShip();
    }
}

public class PriorityOrder : IOrder {
    protected PriorityPlan _priorityPlan;

    @Override
    public int getDaysToShip() {
        return _priorityPlan.getDaysToShip();
    }
}

public class CheatOrder : IOrder {
    private IOrder _order;

    public CheatOrder(IOrder order) {
        _order = order;
    }

    @Override
    public int getDaysToShip() {
        return _order.getDaysToShip() - 1; // Cheating by subtracting 1 day
    }
}
```

**Usage:**

```
// Create a PriorityOrder object
PriorityOrder priorityOrder = new PriorityOrder();

// Create a CheatOrder object that wraps the PriorityOrder object
CheatOrder cheatOrder = new CheatOrder(priorityOrder);

// Get the days to ship for the cheat order
